OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FScotland fans have made a huge impact
OL,8,Fin the US, with the Tartan Army seen
OL,9,Ftaking over Boston before and after
OL,10,Ftheir opening World Cup game against
OL,11,FHaiti.
OL,13,FSupporters were filmed singing and
OL,14,Fdancing in the streets ahead of the
OL,15,Fmatch, and even heard belting out
OL,16,Ftheir favourite football chants during
OL,17,Fa Red Sox baseball game the day after.
OL,19,FAnother tradition they've imported
OL,20,Ffrom Scotland is decorating statues
OL,21,Fwith traffic cones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
