OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FITV News explains where the Scots
OL,8,Fcustom comes from.
OL,10,FWhere did the traffic cones tradition
OL,11,Fstart?
OL,13,FThe tradition started in Glasgow in
OL,14,Fthe 1980s, when a cone was put on the
OL,15,Fhead of a Duke of Wellington statue
OL,16,Foutside the city's Gallery of Modern
OL,17,FArt at night.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
