OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FAuthorities removed the cone, but new
OL,8,Fones kept reappearing every few days
OL,9,Fas others climbed the statue to keep
OL,10,Fthe prank going.
OL,12,FGlasgow City Council battled for years
OL,13,Ftrying to get people to drop the
OL,14,Ftradition, warning that damage was
OL,15,Fbeing caused to the statue and calling
OL,16,Fit an "act of vandalism".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
