OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FIn 2013, it proposed doubling the
OL,8,Fheight of the plinth to deter people
OL,9,Ffrom climbing it, but the plan was
OL,10,Fscrapped after tens of thousands of
OL,11,Fpeople opposed it.
OL,13,FThe council claimed that the cost of
OL,14,Fremoving the cones each time was
OL,15,Faround #10,000 per year, #100 for
OL,16,Fevery removal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
