OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FPolice also tried to warn that anyone
OL,8,Fcaught climbing the statue to place a
OL,9,Fcone at the top would face criminal
OL,10,Fprosecution, but it is not clear if
OL,11,Fanyone has been charged in the last
OL,12,Fdecade.
OL,14,FAre there cones on any other statues
OL,15,Fin Scotland?
OL,17,FEdinburgh has also picked up the
OL,18,Ftrend, with the famous statue of
OL,19,FScottish writer Sir Walter Scott often
OL,20,Fwearing a cone hat in the city.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
