OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FA figurine of philosopher and
OL,8,Fhistorian David Hume has also been
OL,9,Fregularly adorned with a cone.
OL,11,FIn England, cone hats have also
OL,12,Fappeared on sailor Thomas Waghorn in
OL,13,FKent, Queen Victoria in Leamington
OL,14,FSpa, and on a Duke of Wellington
OL,15,Ffigure in Leeds.
OL,17,FWhat have Scots done in the US?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
