OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FTraffic cones have been spotted on top
OL,8,Fof multiple statues in Boston, where
OL,9,FScotland is playing their first two
OL,10,FWorld Cup games.
OL,12,FTwo statues of former US state
OL,13,Frepresentative James Michael Curley
OL,14,Fwere given new orange hats, as well as
OL,15,Fa figure of Canadian ice hockey star
OL,16,FBobby Orr and founding father Samuel
OL,17,FAdams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
