OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FA bronze statue of an octopus holding
OL,8,Fendangered animals in its arms, known
OL,9,Fas "The Arms of Friendship", has seen
OL,10,Fcones placed on each of the creature's
OL,11,Fheads.
OL,13,FThe famous "Mother Duck" and her eight
OL,14,Fducklings in the Boston Public Garden
OL,15,Fsuffered a similar fate, despite the
OL,16,Ftallest of them being only 3ft 2in
OL,17,Ftall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
