OL,3,CWhy are Scottish World Cup fans
OL,4,Cputting traffic cones on Boston's
OL,5,Cstatues?
OL,7,FFans even found a figurine of Scottish
OL,8,Fpoet Robert Burns in Boston's Fenway-
OL,9,FKenmore neighbourhood, which was
OL,10,Fchristened with a cone late at night.
OL,12,FAfter Scotland's next game against
OL,13,FMorocco on June 19, the team will head
OL,14,Fto Miami to face Brazil on June 24.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
